{"id": 1917, "genre": 1001, "title": "根据你的经验，你最怕精彩的刑侦剧走入哪些老套路数？", "description": "一边激动追剧一边暗自祈祷千万别烂尾千万别烂尾。", "record_count": 2625, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201709191014164RaOLwePrXdyF8BW.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-21T03:00:10Z", "options": [{"id": 237056, "content": "嘿嘿", "image": "img/option/option/20170921173340cGnrXsM6KSQf1gvN.jpg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1089402}, {"id": 237058, "content": "没有看到真实的。随他去吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1022071}, {"id": 237060, "content": "男主啥都知道", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 928441}, {"id": 237062, "content": "没有细节，用了神勇而神勇", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137347}, {"id": 237063, "content": "然你心甘情愿被套路\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1098431}, {"id": 237064, "content": "侦探和观众信息不对等", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1004548}, {"id": 237066, "content": "影片前4/5让我猜到结局的都算套路", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 955981}, {"id": 237068, "content": "凶手是个左撇子！", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 474034}, {"id": 237069, "content": "主角团灭，第二部演员垃圾", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1086470}, {"id": 237070, "content": "必须是天才帅气social disorder 大侦探爱上初出茅庐冲动无脑女猪脚的辣鸡套路吖！！！！辣鸡辣鸡辣鸡辣鸡辣鸡辣鸡辣鸡", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 724572}, {"id": 237071, "content": "演尸体的不专业还能看到在动", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137430}, {"id": 237327, "content": "正义永远都是赢家", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138296}, {"id": 237839, "content": "男主角喜欢的女主角的老爹是反派大BOSS ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 692082}, {"id": 243215, "content": "男主为了傻白甜女主一不小心丢失了男二", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163914}, {"id": 237072, "content": "主角智商超高但有心理缺陷，天才嘛，都有心理缺陷吧。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1080561}, {"id": 237073, "content": "男主几乎承担了剧中所有人员的工作\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 908185}, {"id": 237074, "content": "想了半，最终以一种科幻不可能的手法结尾", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137448}, {"id": 237842, "content": "一个人的台词就可以预测到他接下来会被凶手杀掉", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154864}, {"id": 237075, "content": "配角被反派设局套路一筹莫展之时，一定有主角运筹帷幄，洞察一切。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833440}, {"id": 237331, "content": "情人更从容惹我刚发染发", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 402790}, {"id": 237076, "content": "案件调查进入死胡同，就会有一波路人来送助攻", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 833440}, {"id": 237844, "content": "人人的好奇心皆在这里得到满足", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 785370}, {"id": 237077, "content": "网剧十宗罪就是最看不下去的典范，每个人都胸有成竹如同神探上身，连证据都没研究清楚神推理就一套套出来，啧啧啧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 416515}, {"id": 237079, "content": "坏人累都被ko", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 773979}, {"id": 237081, "content": "主角比观众还会上帝视角", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137500}, {"id": 237083, "content": "凶手就是委托人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2093}, {"id": 237339, "content": "看开头知道结果", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138309}, {"id": 237084, "content": "主角怎么 乱搞冷脸发脾气除女主都没人搞定", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1116362}, {"id": 237340, "content": "看开头知道结果", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138309}, {"id": 237086, "content": "从推理破案变成好莱坞动作片", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137542}, {"id": 237087, "content": "主角如果不是领导，那他/她一定会在行动中不听上级命令，后来还绝不认错。有趣的主角光环在于，领导会放过他/她", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1099952}, {"id": 237088, "content": "一直在主角身边的二号角色其实是反派卧底…", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1007288}, {"id": 237090, "content": "当然是喜闻乐见的王警官系列", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057221}, {"id": 237091, "content": "感觉现在的刑侦剧常常为了悬疑而悬疑，特别生硬。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137352}, {"id": 237093, "content": "为凸显主角，其余都智商不上线", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1131500}, {"id": 237094, "content": "第一集，刚从警校毕业的妹子被老司机看轻，不久妹子就展现出过人的本事让老司机刮目相看", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 303059}, {"id": 237095, "content": "疑犯突然智商下线，主角突然智商溢出！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137584}, {"id": 237096, "content": "精分，幻觉，多重人格", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843724}, {"id": 237097, "content": "Boss", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 367752}, {"id": 237098, "content": "开头上龙虾 结尾蛋花汤", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 881217}, {"id": 237357, "content": "嘿嘿嘿嘿嘿", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1138347}, {"id": 237102, "content": "后刑侦为男女主的辅助了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1133170}, {"id": 237103, "content": "最后一刻刀抵在主角脖子上都是主角早已猜到配合犯人的演戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 137354}, {"id": 237104, "content": "主角怎样都不会死", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652118}, {"id": 237105, "content": "莫名其妙的复活", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 652118}, {"id": 237107, "content": "大结局嘴炮的胜利，反派大魔王被主角几句话轰的激动的不能自已，悔恨万分", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 816951}, {"id": 237108, "content": "最怕又是女主被反派绑架，而且明明有很多机会就是不杀死，一直等到主角逆袭", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1121671}, {"id": 237109, "content": "永远有一个大学刚毕业或者菜鸟型角色什么都不会 但是每次都有歪打正着的发生成为破案关键", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 809748}, {"id": 237110, "content": "凶手就在身边", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1123717}, {"id": 237111, "content": "凶手作案的手法与典型案例惊人的相似", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1137705}]}